Creating cryptocurrency based on current block difficulty 
      if current block difficulty is above 20, mint three times as much currency to the user 
      if current block difficulty is below 20, mint one third as much currency to the user 
Creating cryptocurrency based on message data
      if message data is above 25 bytes, mint double the amount of currency to the user 
      if message data is below 12 bytes, mint one fourth the amount of currency to the user 
Ensuring longevity of the coin 
      for every transaction with message data less than 16 bytes, send 1% of reward to the creator 
      if the quantity of currency remaining shrinks below one fourth of the starting amount
          for every transaction with message data greater than 16 bytes, creator sends 0.02% of stored currency to miner 
